林國安、楊耿明、宣大衛、張資宜、梁守謙(2005) 臺南盆地油氣潛能綜合評估。台灣石油地質，37號，第29-56。
Lin, K.-A. Yang, K.-M. Hsiuan, T.-H. Chang, T.-Y. and Kiang, S.-C.(2005) Integrated Assessment of Hydrocarbon Potential in the TainanBasin. Petroleum Geology of Taiwan, 37, 29-56.
傅式齊、楊育良、黃昌盛、陳建文、宣大衛(2005)震幅支距分析與模擬應用於東引島盆地油氣潛能評估。台灣石油地質，37號，第57-78頁。
Futh, S.-C. Yang, Y.-L. Huang, C.-S. Cheng, C.-W. and Hsian, T.-H. (2005)AVO Analysis and Modeling Applied to Hydrocarbon Potential Assessment of the TongyingtaoBasin. Petroleum Geology of Taiwan, 37.57-78.
張資宜、梁守謙、邱瑞琅、楊育良、薑智文(2005) 震測資料逆推處理與其應用實例分析研究。台灣石油地質，37號，第79-96頁。
Chang, T.-Y. Liang, S.-C. Chiu, J.-L. Yang, Y.-L. and Chiang, C.-W.(2005) Seismic Inversion Methodology and Application for Lithology Prediction. Petroleum Geology of Taiwan, 37,79-96.
林國安、李長之、黃旭燦、郭政隆、張資宜、邱仲信、吳素慧(2005) 新竹外海及陸地上地質資料整合研究。台灣石油地質，37號，第97-122頁。
Lin, K.-A. Lee, C.-J. Huang, S.-T. Kuo, C.-L. Chang, T.-Y. Chiu, J.-H. and Wu, S.-H.(2005) Integrated Research of Geological Data in the Hsinchu Area, Offshore and Onshore. Petroleum Geology of Taiwan, 37, 97-122.
徐祥宏、林人仰、楊耿明、黃旭燦、丁信修、楊育良(2005)寶山─竹東地區震測模擬與重合前深度移位。台灣石油地質，37號，第123-136頁。
Hsu, S.-H. Lin, J.-Y. Yang, K.-M. Huang, S.-T. Ting, H.-H. and Yang, Y.-L.(2005) Seismic Modeling and Pre-stack Depth Migration in Pausan-Chutung Area.Petroleum Geology of Taiwan, 37,123-13.
 
 
 
 
 
 





